
The aim of this paper is to enable those who have never reconstructed a zzso to do so from zzso The paper does not attempt to be a comprehensive theoretical guide, but describes one rigorous way of obtaining zzso zzso Those who follow the methods outlined should be able to understand the basic ideas behind the steps taken, the meaning of the zzso trees obtained and the scope of questions that can be answered with zzso zzso The protocols have been successfully tested by volunteers with no zzso zzso 

